        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"intro-content-wrapper\">\n  <h1>The LoamLabs Story</h1>\n  <p>LoamLabs wasn't born in a boardroom; it was born on the trail. We're a team of passionate, lifelong cyclists who spent years searching for the perfect wheelset—one that could withstand the toughest rides and still feel light and responsive. After building countless custom wheels for ourselves and our friends, we turned our obsession with performance and precision into a profession.</p>\n</div>",
